<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="id46ac9739-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior section 6116 was renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t26/s6117">section 6117 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
